description.en: Crypto whales dominate the markets: the VCs, the hedge funds, Wall Street, the crypto OGs and insiders. They get tokens at a discounted price. They get special privileges. They talk directly to the project creators. They buy low and sell high and dump on you. It’s time to fight back. We’re arming the token rebels. The average Joe trader. The retail buyer. The speculator. The small guy. The baby WHALES. Because one day, you’ll become a whale too. Just like WhaleStats gave you the tools to learn from the whales and copy their trades, $BabyWhale gives you the token to turn the tables.
